high_descs: Turn left, take a few step, turn right, and walk around the counter and face the tomato.
Take the tomato on the counter.
Turn around and walk to the sink on the right.
Put the tomato in the sink.
Take the knife on the left side of the sink.
Slice the tomato in the sink.
Place the knife next to the tomato.
Take a slice from the tomato.
Put the slice back in the sink, turn the water on, then turn it off. Take the slice from the sink.
Turn around, take a few steps then turn left and walk to the table on the right.
Put the tomato slice on the table.
anns.task_desc: Place a rinsed tomato slice on the table.

high_descs: Turn 90 degrees to the left, then 90 degrees to the right, then another 90 degrees to the right, and walk to the corner of the counter.
Pick up the tomato on the counter.
Turn around 180 degrees and walk towards the sink.
Place the tomato in the sink.
Pick up the knife on the counter.
Slice the tomato in the sink.
Put the knife in the sink.
Take the tomato slice out of the sink.
Put the tomato slice back in the sink and fill it with water
Take the slice out of the sink and walk to the table in the corner of the room.
Put the tomato slice on the table.
anns.task_desc: Wash a piece of tomato you sliced from a full tomato.

high_descs: Turn left and begin walking across the room, then turn right and start walking, hang a left and walk over to the tomato on the counter.
Pick up the tomato off of the counter.
Turn around and walk forward, then hang a right and walk up to the sink.
Place the tomato in the back left corner of the sink basin.
Pick up the metal butter knife closest to the sink basin.
Slice up the tomato that is in the sink basin.
Put the knife handle down into the middle of the sink basin.
Pick up a piece of sliced tomato out of the sink basin.
Put the piece of sliced tomato into the sink basin, then turn on the water, after a couple seconds turn the water off and remove the tomato slice.
Turn right and walk over to the counter, then turn right again and walk around the counter to the round wooden table in the corner of the room.
Put the clean tomato slice on the table just below the closest book.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean tomato slice on a round table.

high_descs: Go around to the other side of the counter that you are standing in front of.
Pick up the tomato that is on the counter.
Turn around and head to the sink that will be on your right.
Put the tomato in the sink.
Pick up the butter knife that is on the left of the sink.
Use the butter knife to slice the tomato.
Put the butter knife in the sink to the right of the tomato.
Pick up a slice of tomato.
Put the slice of tomato in the sink on the right side of the butter knife, the turn the faucet on and let the sink fill water then empty.
Take the tomato out of the sink, turn around and head to the round table on the other side of the kitchen.
Put the slice of tomato on the table between the book and whole tomato.
anns.task_desc: Put a slice of tomato on the table.
